Distribution of prices

Low budget travellers do not need to fear for the quality of their accomodation : Boston has many areas with excellent ratings and low rents.

        0%        25%        50%        75%       100%

As we can see, the lowest quantile fees correspond to less than 33.33 a night per person. Lets find out below in which areas they are found.
